Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.60,0:01:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.34,0:01:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請往這邊走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.17,0:01:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.78,0:01:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菜點好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.38,0:01:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時，裕美為什麼會在那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.05,0:01:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像也認識植田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們之間 發生過什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.66,0:01:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我想點菜耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.36,0:02:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有在聽嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是，樂意之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.53,0:02:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.47,0:02:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要烤雞串跟生魚片拼盤\N還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.77,0:02:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是，樂意之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.51,0:02:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#22 ちぃ，更衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.15,0:02:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.05,0:02:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐究竟上哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.93,0:02:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.89,0:02:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.16,0:02:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來，秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.53,0:02:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.80,0:02:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家幫我看家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.94,0:02:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子咕嚕咕嚕叫了\N吃飯時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.01,0:02:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不了\N我今晚得用功唸書才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.08,0:02:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明肚子餓卻又不吃飯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒錢嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜中了是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹你沒錢嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.76,0:03:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ用奇洛如賺來的錢\N煮飯給你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ想看到秀樹的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.68,0:03:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 發現一間不錯的餐廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定會喜歡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.92,0:03:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.29,0:03:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛不錯\N料理當然也很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.46,0:03:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，好期待喔\N那是什麼樣的料理？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.53,0:03:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，他們為什麼要握手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.37,0:03:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那不是握手\N是牽手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要牽手呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.97,0:03:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，大概這樣感覺比較幸福吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.01,0:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸福？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.95,0:04:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牽誰都會幸福嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是誰都好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.45,0:04:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是跟喜歡的人才好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牽手的幸福…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們到了，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.14,0:04:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.99,0:04:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.99,0:04:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？都沒人在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.83,0:04:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.67,0:04:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，本…本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像嚇到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.64,0:05:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，因為我在 發呆，是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ來打工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請妳先到裡面去換衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.23,0:05:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一副無精打彩的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.27,0:05:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多了啦，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.11,0:05:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有ちぃ來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我工作也輕鬆了不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.51,0:05:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.48,0:05:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我幫得上忙的話\N請儘管說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.72,0:05:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在ちぃ失蹤時\N願意聽我訴苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我感覺舒坦多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫你的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然算不上是什麼報恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.03,0:06:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我真的沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過我比較笨拙罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.58,0:06:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明想讓\N喜歡的人常保笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻一直害她落淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.72,0:06:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.26,0:06:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ換好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.23,0:06:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.40,0:06:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…ちぃ，那件衣服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.30,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，不是那件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.61,0:06:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.88,0:06:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件衣服是為別人準備的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.01,0:06:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直捨不得丟掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.85,0:06:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ弄錯了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.32,0:06:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都要怪我沒收好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.32,0:06:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ的衣服在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.62,0:07:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，ちぃ就麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.62,0:07:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.93,0:07:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.84,0:07:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.21,0:07:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑步是我最得意的項目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.32,0:08:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦真的比較好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.12,0:08:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦比人類的女孩子還好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件衣服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.49,0:08:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明說是為我而做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓電腦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.77,0:08:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那ちぃ所穿的那件制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是裕美的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.85,0:08:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡會痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.05,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過店長的表情\N看起來好像很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.86,0:08:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又讓她流淚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還猶豫要不要追過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長，你說錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.87,0:08:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是ちぃ弄哭裕美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看到ちぃ後就哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.71,0:08:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.28,0:08:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她明明很清楚的\N跟我說了“再見”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.99,0:09:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻一直藕斷絲連…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.24,0:09:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.74,0:09:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.18,0:09:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切換至留話機模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.08,0:09:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錄音完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.59,0:09:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍手呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.69,0:09:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.46,0:09:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.86,0:09:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉工作做完了\N要拍手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛要我拍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.53,0:09:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.17,0:09:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的電腦都好怪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是ちぃ還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.68,0:10:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.22,0:10:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有客人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能安靜點嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.09,0:10:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.10,0:10:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“再見”的意思是“不能在身旁”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“再也見不到面”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“非常…非常痛苦的事”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.18,0:10:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長這裡會痛是因為“再見”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是裕美說“再見”的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.12,0:10:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.42,0:10:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論誰說“再見”\N這裡都會痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.29,0:10:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪種“再見”都一樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.76,0:10:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論被誰說這種話\N都會感到寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.77,0:11:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摯愛的人所說的“再見”\N是最痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.21,0:11:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾在奇洛如打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為植田店長\N是個非常好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.85,0:11:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空就會教我做蛋糕與餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.72,0:11:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長真的是個溫柔的好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,容易臉紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.70,0:11:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就喜歡上他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.57,0:11:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我鼓起了勇氣向他告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.78,0:11:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.18,0:11:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個，我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.78,0:11:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.55,0:11:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.62,0:11:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.49,0:12:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件制服也是專為裕美做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.46,0:12:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望妳能一直做下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.17,0:12:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.21,0:12:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比裕美年長不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經離過婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你結過婚嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過她已經過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.55,0:12:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡離過婚的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.59,0:12:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.03,0:12:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.36,0:12:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很在意\N店長曾與什麼樣的人結過婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.17,0:12:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是便偷偷地\N用電腦查了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.51,0:12:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，能麻煩你幫我在網上\N搜尋一下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.48,0:12:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，絲茉茉，妳可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.05,0:12:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以，請輸入關鍵字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搜索文字是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田弘康，蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.02,0:13:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇洛如，結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.62,0:13:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現158筆資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.16,0:13:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中有幾個新聞網站\N可以收看影片？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.66,0:13:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.06,0:13:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.93,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想在電視上放出來\N可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.13,0:13:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.24,0:13:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，請將這個與電視連線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.04,0:13:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棟建築物的電話線夠用嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.84,0:13:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？會有問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.65,0:13:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,播放動態影片時\N如果線路頻寬不夠的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.95,0:13:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就得花很多時間下載…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.95,0:13:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，好像沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始播放第一筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.86,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當您決定與電腦結婚時\N會感到不安嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有…有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.73,0:13:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直煩惱著\N婚後是否能為她帶來幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.41,0:13:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過世間有許多種的夫婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,縱使與他人不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.78,0:14:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們能一點一滴地\N製造屬於我們的幸福就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.38,0:14:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像講了奇怪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始播放第二筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.49,0:14:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您與電腦的婚姻生活\N在車禍後告了一個段落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.69,0:14:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您現在的感想是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.16,0:14:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦真的救了您一命嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您有打算再與電腦結婚嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您打算將電腦火化嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是要廢棄掉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.07,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.37,0:14:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦等於是您的救命恩人對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請別將她與別的混為一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.91,0:14:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子是有名字的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫“裕美”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.59,0:14:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看了以後就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.46,0:14:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比不上她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.30,0:14:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.80,0:14:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美好像也很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.90,0:15:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從眼睛流出很多水來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.47,0:15:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.84,0:15:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是指眼淚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會流淚呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在高興或是悲傷時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.72,0:15:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美是因為高興而流淚的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.29,0:15:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因為傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.92,0:15:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她曾說過\N跟我在一起會感到悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.36,0:15:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是因為她討厭我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.53,0:15:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想在一起的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.90,0:15:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼裕美會在店門口呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.00,0:15:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會在討厭的人附近呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.77,0:15:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.64,0:15:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美常常在那裡朝店裡看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直看著店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一臉痛苦的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.45,0:15:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過剛剛不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.45,0:15:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在看到ちぃ穿這件衣服後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.32,0:15:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美的眼裡流下好多眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到這件衣服後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.93,0:15:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是裕美的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.20,0:16:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼裕美看到ちぃ\N穿這件衣服後會傷心 呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長表情好痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.84,0:16:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦與悲傷\N該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長你想怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.54,0:16:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.82,0:16:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，我想請妳幫個忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.02,0:16:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.02,0:16:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到可能被拿來與她比較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.49,0:16:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得很害怕，很難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.60,0:16:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不像電腦一樣萬能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.00,0:16:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就先跟他說再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.94,0:16:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.74,0:16:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在比分手前還更痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.71,0:16:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.68,0:16:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳真的很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.72,0:16:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳真的愛上植田了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像我哥哥喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.80,0:17:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我覺得植田應該也很難受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.93,0:17:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他前妻是台電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不認為他有意玩弄妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.27,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.91,0:17:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為店長就是那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.28,0:17:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說，如果他回應了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.15,0:17:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想他對妳是真心 的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.88,0:17:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長對於他妻子的事\N應該感到很痛苦才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.99,0:17:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他還是喜歡上了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.89,0:17:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這點很了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.03,0:17:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想他應該不會\N特別把妳拿去跟他前妻比較的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.30,0:17:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的話\N你不會在意嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.11,0:17:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.84,0:17:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該…會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.78,0:17:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我不會比較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.18,0:17:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果別人這麼對我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.58,0:17:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會感到很痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.12,0:18:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我認為\N店長也不會那麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.03,0:18:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.76,0:18:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.70,0:18:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.16,0:18:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道我們在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.90,0:18:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我請ちぃ幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.24,0:18:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經由讀取裕美的\N攜帶型電腦的編號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請她幫我找到\N你們所在的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.71,0:18:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它明明沒 發出聲音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.45,0:18:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，忽然跑來打擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.62,0:18:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說，請進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.83,0:18:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，都是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.87,0:18:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長你沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.07,0:18:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有好好地說明的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.01,0:18:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會讓裕美如此落淚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.78,0:19:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會與“裕美”結婚\N是因為“她是她”的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.05,0:19:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是因為她是電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.75,0:19:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我因為“裕美是裕美”\N而喜歡上妳是一樣的道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.36,0:19:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“裕美”…“裕美”她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.66,0:19:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然電腦看似完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.73,0:19:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事只有電腦才辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有些事卻只有人類才辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.24,0:19:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這與身為人類才能辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.75,0:19:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是因為是人類\N而辦不到的情況是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.75,0:19:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾以為\N自己無法再愛上任何人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.09,0:19:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是不會再度愛上電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.23,0:19:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.79,0:19:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算裕美是台電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該還是會愛上妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.47,0:19:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，抱歉\N我又把妳弄哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.47,0:20:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.08,0:20:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.74,0:20:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ穿錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.58,0:20:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長說這是裕美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.92,0:20:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長…那個…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.43,0:20:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.03,0:20:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.13,0:20:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.30,0:20:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你愛上我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.43,0:21:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事只有電腦才辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.50,0:21:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有些事卻只有人類才辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.80,0:21:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這與身為人類才能辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.31,0:21:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是因為是人類\N而辦不到的情況是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算裕美是台電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.68,0:21:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該還是會愛上妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.69,0:21:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.49,0:21:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牽手會覺得幸福嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.33,0:21:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.64,0:21:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她決定好了\N“只屬於我的人”了是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.15,0:21:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子不去是不行的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.75,0:21:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然希望會有個好結局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.68,0:21:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.99,0:21:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.70,0:22:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街道如同深海般寂靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.78,0:22:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綿延的路上卻只有我孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.96,0:22:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循著遠方的聲音向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.13,0:22:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷找尋著一閃即逝的藍色光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.72,0:23:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.13,0:23:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後不再遺忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.20,0:23:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有多心 痛         也要在你身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.85,0:23:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到永遠         直到永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.69,0:23:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心 中只能容納一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.33,0:23:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他露出笑容\N我就會感到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.23,0:23:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他陪伴在我身旁\N我就會感到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.91,0:23:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，只要他感到幸福\N我就會感到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.08,0:23:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與他人不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.51,0:24:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.51,0:24:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最特別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.98,0:24:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.62,0:24:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits         下一回\N「ちぃ，決定」
